    public static class TikzGraphicalFeatureModelFormat.TikZBodyFormat
extends de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.io.APersistentFormat<IGraphicalFeatureModel>
    Creates the body for the LaTeX export.

    Note: For exporting purposes the file name must be body.tex and exported in the same folder as the main file. This file runs only with the head file and the main file.
